title: Palestinians, Israeli troops clash on Nakba day
text:
Palestinians, Israeli troops clash on Nakba day 1:06pm EDT - 00:48
Palestinians clashed with Israeli forces in the West Bank during Nakba or ''catastrophe'' day when hundreds of thousands of Palestinians were dispossessed when the state of Israel was created. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
